snippet.title: AMBER HEARD AND JOHNNY DEPP AUDIO SURFACES ONLINE | Double Toasted
snippet.description:
AMBER HEARD AND JOHNNY DEPP AUDIO SURFACES ONLINE | Double Toasted - The Double Toasted podcast give their reaction to a video that transcribes the audio of a fight between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard, where inadvertently Amber Heard admits to hitting Depp. Is this enough to allege that Amber was abusive to Johnny? Could this effect the sequel to Aquaman or any work that Amber has in the future? Will we be looking at these interviews with a different perspective? Let us know what you think down below!
